AKA 422 : http://vanillaforums.org/profile/34127/422

This is a silent pure css smiley / emoticon plugin. I am not a great lover of lots of images on forums, and where possible we like to use css.

This plugin uses code from : (c) 2010 Steve Schwartz (JangoSteve) and is modified by us for Vanilla.

The codes for the smileys are:

:-) :) :o) :c) :^) :-D :-( :-9 ;-) :-P :-p :-b :-O :-/ :-X :-# :'( B-) 8-) :-\ ;*( :-* :] :> =] =) 8) :} :D 8D XD xD =D :( :< :[ :{ =( ;) ;] ;D :P :p =P =p :b :O 8O :/ =/ :S :# :X B) O:)

and some special ones:

<3 ;( >:) >;) >:( O_o O_O o_o 0_o T_T ^_^ ?-) [+=..]

Have fun, uses css3 so Chrome and FF support only.